&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Yahoo CEO Marissa Mayer loses bonus, top lawyer resigns in wake of massive&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TODAYonline The disclosure last year by Yahoo of two massive user-data breaches that occurred in 2013 and 2014 led Verizon to lop US$350 million (S$493.1 &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.todayonline.com/business/yahoo-ceo-marissa-mayer-loses-bonus-top-lawyer-resigns-wake-massive-security-breaches&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.todayonline.com/business/yahoo-ceo-marissa-mayer-loses-bonus-top-lawyer-resigns-wake-massive-security-breaches&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Yahoo GC Steps Down, CEO Loses Bonus After Data Breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;paid her annual bonus for 2016 in the wake of an internal probe that &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.lexisnexis.com/legalnewsroom/privacy/b/newsheadlines/archive/2017/03/02/yahoo-gc-steps-down-ceo-loses-bonus-after-data-breaches.aspx&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.lexisnexis.com/legalnewsroom/privacy/b/newsheadlines/archive/2017/03/02/yahoo-gc-steps-down-ceo-loses-bonus-after-data-breaches.aspx&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;IBM Says Cloud Computing Security is Less Susceptible to Attacks If Done&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1redDrop (blog) The report goes on to say that data breaches can cause companies to lose customers, and this phenomenon is more acute in financial services, &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://1reddrop.com/2017/03/03/ibm-cloud-computing-security-less-susceptible-attacks-done-right/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://1reddrop.com/2017/03/03/ibm-cloud-computing-security-less-susceptible-attacks-done-right/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

