&lt;p&gt;connect i keeps offline. I have tried different firewall rules, application &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://community.sophos.com/products/unified-threat-management/f/endpoint-protection-antivirus-and-device-control/89333/whatsapp-won-t-connect-sophos-umt-9/324503&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://community.sophos.com/products/unified-threat-management/f/endpoint-protection-antivirus-and-device-control/89333/whatsapp-won-t-connect-sophos-umt-9/324503&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Cybereason Signs OEM Agreement with OPSWAT to Leverage Metadefender Threat&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PR Web (press release) Cybereason is the leader in endpoint protection, offering endpoint detection and response, next-generation antivirus, and managed monitoring &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.prweb.com/releases/2017/03/prweb14117217.htm&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.prweb.com/releases/2017/03/prweb14117217.htm&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Yahoo CEO Punished for Data Breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The data breaches, reported by Yahoo in 2016, compromised over 1 billion user accounts and cost the company $350 million after Verizon reduced its &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.darkreading.com/careers-and-people/yahoo-ceo-punished-for-data-breaches/d/d-id/1328309&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.darkreading.com/careers-and-people/yahoo-ceo-punished-for-data-breaches/d/d-id/1328309&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

