&lt;p&gt;Combining a robust suite of endpoint detection and analysis capabilities by leveraging a single endpoint sensor and an open, scalable multi-tenant &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20170303005394/en/CounterTack-Digital-DNA%C2%AE-Earns-Stars-SC-Media%E2%80%99s&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20170303005394/en/CounterTack-Digital-DNA%C2%AE-Earns-Stars-SC-Media%E2%80%99s&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

