&lt;p&gt;million records in the first two months of 2017, the Identity Theft Resource &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.smartbrief.com/s/2017/03/more-1m-records-exposed-so-far-2017-data-breaches&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.smartbrief.com/s/2017/03/more-1m-records-exposed-so-far-2017-data-breaches&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

